  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to compare between standard versus comprehensive care for post-acute
      kidney injury who are admitted with acute kidney injury at least stage 2 or receive renal
      replacement therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
